TRASTA TO LAUNCH ANOTHER COMPANY THIS YEAR . Commercial bank Trasta Bank said on Wednesay that it would place the shares of another private company in the same way that it is issuing those of insurance company Balta . " We hope that in autumn 1997 and during 1998 several other companies will go a similar way , " Trasta vice - chairman Aldis Reims told a news conference . " At the moment , Trasta is finalising an agreement for placing a new issue with a Latvian company , which will take place in October or November this year , " he added . Trasta is to issue 200 , 000 shares or 6 . 5 percent of Balta ' s share capital . - - Riga newsroom , + 371 721 5240 
